name: android-data-management-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for data management and persistence in Android
globs: **/*.{kt,java,xml}

- Use Room for local database
- Implement repository pattern for data access
- Use DataStore or SharedPreferences for user preferences
- Implement proper data caching strategy
- Use Retrofit for network requests
- Implement offline-first approach when possible
- Handle database migrations correctly
- Optimize database queries
- Implement pagination for large datasets
- Use WorkManager for background tasks and scheduling
- Implement proper data validation
- Use proper encryption for sensitive data 